Kassiopeia Guide README File
----------------------------

Instructions for adding documentation
 1. Find the .tex file for the part of Kassiopeia you want to document.
 2. Put your documentation (in LaTeX format) in that file
   2a. Define any new commands you want to use frequently in KSGuide.tex, where indicated.
 3. Put your references (in BibTeX format) in KSGuide.bib.
 4. Make sure you are on the author list (in KSGuide.tex)
 5. Test compile the full guide and correct any mistakes. Repeat this step until it works.